text.tspan: We need a transaction to initialize the thoth network,this will enable some operations to be undertaken by any user with lovelace,
Here are examples of These operations: Mint (a bunch of) tokens (Maybe); Update my script address with the latest associated network details;
change the datum of a token in the thoth network address after its been created; The initialization can be done by anyone with a valid
pubkeyhash and some Ada to pay transaction fees and minAda for token transfers.
